                     <interp inst="t17770910-9-person155" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am a pawnbroker: I took in pawn a silk handkerchief of the prisoner for two shillings.</p>
               <p>[It was produced in Court, and deposed to by the prosecutor.]</p>
               <p>Prosecutor. It is my nephew's, it is marked with his name.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17770910-9-person156">
