             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am a pawnbroker: I took in a handkerchief of the prisoner (it is produced).</p>
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="177709100019"></xptr>Prosecutor. That is mine; my face bled and I had it in my pocket several days; I can swear to it.</p>
               <p>'The prisoner did not say any thing in his defence.'</p>
